<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Wilhelm<ex>m</ex></expan>, <expan>graf<ex>en</ex></expan> von
                        Orlamünd, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> zu Lewenstein </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als uns ewr gnade
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von ein ewrs armmans,
                                <expan>H<ex>er</ex>man</expan> Schobers, und
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>gesess<ex>en</ex></expan> zum guldin
                        ring, etc., das haben wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und haben
                                <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, <expan>gena<ex>n</ex>t</expan> der
                                <expan>Hawsma<ex>n</ex></expan>, umb <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> besandt und <expan>sov<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
                        mit im geredt, daz er uns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> hat,
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> selb schriftlich
                            <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> zu
                            <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t<ex>en</ex></expan>, wie er die sache gehandelt
                        hab. Dewcht <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> den
                            <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>armman<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz er <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> zu
                        dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> icht <expan>zu spreche<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hett</expan>, so <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir im
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan> schein <expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan> mit
                                <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gwalt <expan>frewntl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
                        slewnigs <expan>recht<ex>en</ex>l</expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>helff<ex>en</ex></expan> vor des reichs
                            <expan>richt<ex>er</ex></expan> bey uns zu
                            <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan>, wenn wir des ermant
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>, so der
                            <expan>obg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> bey uns anheim ist
                            <expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lich</expan>; und ob
                            <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>armman<ex>n</ex></expan> in den <expan>nehst<ex>en</ex></expan> vier
                                <expan>woche<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> zu uns <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> wil, so
                        sol er <expan>dies<ex>elb</ex></expan> zeit zu und von uns für uns und die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> on <expan>gev<ex>er</ex>de</expan>
                        iiii tag geleyt <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>ip<ex>s</ex>a</expan> die <expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan>
<expan>Joh<ex>ann</ex>is</expan>
<expan>ewan<ex>gelis</ex><hi rend="sup">te</hi></expan> xxiii<hi rend="sup">o</hi>. </ab>
